stay → stays       thank → thanks
find → finds       laugh → laughs
stop → stops       match → matches
put → puts         guess → guesses
test → tests       change → changes
do → does          go → goes
create → creates   relax → relaxes
travel → travels   interview → interviews

** Slide 8
Правопис дієслів на -Y у 3 особі однини

pay → pays        buy → buys
fly → flies       enjoy → enjoys
study → studies   say → says
play → plays      worry → worries
marry → marries   carry → carries

